# Git Safety Rules

**Last updated:** {{DATE}}

## Forbidden Commands on Main

```bash
git reset --hard
git clean -fd
git stash
git push --force
--no-verify
```

## Safe Commands

```bash
git status
git log
git diff
git add .
git commit -m "message"
```

## Merge Strategy

Use `pnpm wu:done` for all merges. Never merge manually.
